Package: postgresql-9.4-osml10n-kanjitranslit
Conflicts: postgresql-9.4-kanjitranslit
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, postgresql-9.4
Description: stored procedure kanji transcription for PostgreSQL using kakasi library
 Using this library one will be able to issue queries like the following
 |                                                               
 |mydb=>  select osml10n_kanji_transcript('漢字');
 | osml10n_kanji_transcript
 |---------------
 | kanji
 |(1 row)
